start.label: wait for other shoe to drop
grass is always greener on other side

examples.en: The house is in a highly desirable location.
It is not desirable to overbalance the budget
The experiment did not achieve a desirable result.
A high level of biodiversity is desirable.
But personal prejudices again interposed to prevent an arrangement so desirable.
The most desirable feature of the park are the beautiful views.
It is desirable that the preservation of accidentals should be seen in proper perspective.
Add a desirable note of specificity to the discussion.
She claims that the average person ingests considerably more calories than is necessary or desirable.
